extends layout
block content 
    h2=header_message
    p This task is part of a research study conducted by Dr. Lior Fink.   
    h3 Purpose
    p The purpose of the research is to investigate online behavior.   
    h3 Procedure  
    p Next you will be redirected to a webpage in which you will be asked to perform a digital task, followed by a set of questions. The expected duration of participation is approximately 7 minutes.   
    h3 Participant Requirements 
    p Participation in this study is limited to individuals age 18 and older.
    h3 Risk 
    p The risks and discomfort associated with participation in this study are no greater than those ordinarily encountered in daily life or during other online activities. 
    h3 Benefits 
    p There may be no personal benefit from your participation in the study, however, the knowledge received may be of value to the general understanding of online behavior. 
    h3 Compensation and Costs 
    p You will be compensated for your time, as mentioned in Prolific. There will be no cost to you if you participate in this study. 
    h3 Future Use of Information 
    p In the future once we have removed all identifiable information from your data, we may use it for our research studies, or we may distribute the data to other researchers for their research studies. We would do this without getting additional informed consent from you. Sharing of data with other researchers will only be done in such a manner that you will not be identified.
    h3 Confidentiality 
    p The data captured for the research does not include any personally identifiable information about you. Your IP address will not be captured.
    h3 Right to Ask Questions and Contact Information
    p If you have any questions about this study, you should feel free to ask them by contacting the Principal Investigator now at finkl@bgu.ac.il . If you have questions later, desire additional information, or wish to withdraw your participation, please contact the Principal Investigator by e-mail in accordance with the contact information listed above. 
    h3 Voluntary Participation 
    p Your participation in this research is voluntary. You may discontinue participation at any time during the research activity. You may print a copy of this consent form for your records. 

    form(id="consenrForm", method='POST' action='/consent')
        table 
            tr
                td 
                    span I am age 18 or older.
                td
                    input(type='radio', id="18YES", class="radio_selection", name="consent.age", value="YES", required)
                    label(for="18YES") Yes
                td
                    input(type='radio', id="18NO", class="radio_selection", name="consent.age", value="NO")
                    label(for="18NO") No  
            tr 
                td
                    span I have read and understood the information above. 
                td 
                    input(type='radio', id="informYES", class="radio_selection", name="consent.inform", value="YES", required)
                    label(for="informYES") Yes
                td
                    input(type='radio', id="informNO", class="radio_selection", name="consent.inform", value="NO")
                    label(for="informNO") No 
            tr 
                td
                    span I want to participate in this research and continue with the task.
                td
                    input(type='radio', id="consentYES", class="radio_selection", name="consent.consent", value="YES", required)
                    label(for="consentYES") Yes 
                td
                    input(type='radio', id="consentNO", class="radio_selection", name="consent.consent", value="NO")
                    label(for="consentNO") No 
            tr
                td
                    input(id="consentSubmit", type="submit", value="Submit")
